        .patient-journal__content Bacon ipsum dolor sit amet bacon doner ball tip, tri-tip porchetta ground round pork chop short loin. Chuck pork chop swine hamburger sirloin meatloaf. Shankle chicken ham jowl tenderloin. Kevin doner sirloin tail tongue pork loin sausage meatball.

        button.patient-journal__copypast-button
            span Copy/Past